# Voice design (Flutter UI)

Before editing UI under `src/frontend/lib/ui/` or `lib/shell/`:

1. Read [docs/design/brand.md](docs/design/brand.md), [docs/design/tokens.md](docs/design/tokens.md), and [design/tokens/voice.tokens.json](design/tokens/voice.tokens.json).
2. **MUST** use `VoiceColors.of(context)`, `Theme.of(context).colorScheme` (built from tokens), and widgets in `lib/ui/core/`.
3. **MUST NOT** add `ColorScheme.fromSeed`, `Colors.indigo`, or `Color(0x…)` in `lib/ui/**` or `lib/shell/**` (only `lib/theme/` may define resolved colors).
4. Visual constant changes **MUST** update `design/tokens/voice.tokens.json` and `src/frontend/assets/design/voice.tokens.json` in the same PR (`make design-tokens-check`).
5. **Profile accent** is per active profile (`profileAccent.defaults` + optional override); primary CTA and send use accent; lists/rail stay neutral.
6. Penpot MCP read is optional; do not invent hex — use tokens. Frame IDs/URLs: [docs/design/screens.md](docs/design/screens.md). Setup: [docs/design/penpot-setup.md](docs/design/penpot-setup.md).
